Prerequisites:
- NodeJS
- MongoDB 
Steps:
- Clone the project
- Go the project folder
npm install
node app

APIs:
- /create : Create the SMS template
- /getAllTemplates : List all the templates from the MongoDB
- /getTemplateByID/:id : Get a particular template by passing its id
- /deleteByID/:id : Delete a template from MongoDB
- /update/:id : Upate a template
- /createDynamicSMS/:id : Create dynamic SMS. If the dynamic text is a url, shorten the url and send the shortend url as response
